  m_text: 'CROSS THE UPPER GAPS     FALLS LEAD TO THE SPIKE RAMP     SLIDE TO THE
    BOTTOM TO RETRY

    CONTROLLER: STICK / D-PAD MOVE  |  A RUN + B JUMP = POWER
    JUMP  |  X INTERACT / PARACHUTE  |  Y POTION  |  START PAUSE  |  BACK / SELECT
    SHOP  |  REMAP: OVERVIEW > CONTROLS

    KEYBOARD: ARROWS / A-D MOVE  |  SHIFT
    RUN + SPACE JUMP  |  UP / W INTERACT / PARACHUTE  |  H POTION  |  ESC PAUSE 
    |  BACKSPACE SHOP'
